title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland-Alameda County Coliseum on 1993-02-21
description:
Set 1

Bertha-> Greatest Story Ever Told, Lazy River Road, Eternity, Ramble On Rose, Queen Jane Approximately, Row Jimmy, Promised Land

Set 2

Liberty, Corinna-> Crazy Fingers-> Estimated Prophet-> Samson & Delilah, Drums-> Jam-> The Wheel-> I Need A Miracle-> Morning Dew, E: U.S. Blues
